Beginner Guide
</span>

<h1>
Medical Device Basics
</h1>

<p>

Learn the fundamentals of medical devices, their classifications,
regulations, life cycle, safety requirements and quality systems.

This guide is designed for Biomedical Engineers, Regulatory Affairs
Professionals, QA Engineers and Students.

</p>

<div class="buttons">

<a href="/learn/device-classification" class="primary">
Next Topic →
</a>

<a href="/downloads" class="secondary">
Download Templates
</a>

</div>

</div>

